title: Arabic TV Android
description:
By this app you will able to view High Quality TV programs across Arabian Countries. 

Specification of this app:
1. Smooth streaming of HD channels.
2. High Quality of videos for 3G connection.
3. Channels of news, comedy, action, music, movie etc.
4. Channesls from Saudi Arabia, Morocco, Saudi, Qatar, UAE, Kuwait, Syria, Lebanon, Egypt, ALGERIA, Iraq, TUNISIA etc.

Features of this app:
+No Flash Player Required.
+No sign-up required.
+Full Screen viewing.
+Channels updated time to time.

Wait for a while if stream does not initiate immediately. It takes few seconds sometimes to stream a TV link.

DISCLAIMER:

The channels provided in this app is available in public domain. If any copyright claim is there, please mail us.
